  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Users can interact with your ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "Reality Composer",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": " scenes in a number of different ways",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "without you having to explicitly code for them using Reality Composer’s behaviors.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "You can, for example, allow a user’s touch to affect objects in your scene, or let",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "objects respond when the user moves close to them.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Reality Composer includes a number of behavior presets that let you easily add common",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "forms of interactivity to your scene. You can also build your own custom behaviors",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "or use a preset as a starting point for building more complex behaviors. For more",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/building-custom-behaviors",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-a-behavior-preset",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add a behavior preset",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Reality Composer provides six behavior presets that simplify adding common forms",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "of interactivity to your scenes. If any objects in your scene are selected when you",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "add a behavior from a preset, the new behavior is automatically configured to affect",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the selected object or objects. This list describes each of the behavior presets:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Causes one or more objects to animate by jumping up and spinning around in response to user taps",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Tap & Flip",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Plays a sound in response to user taps",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Tap & Play Sound",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Applies a force to objects that simulate physics in response to user taps",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Tap & Add Force",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Causes one or more objects to be invisible when the scene starts",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Start Hidden",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Causes one or more objects to start as invisible, then become visible after a specified duration",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Wait & Show",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Causes one or more objects to jiggle in response to the viewer getting close to it",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Proximity & Jiggle",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "type": "termList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To add a behavior preset to your scene, select the object or objects you want as",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the target of the behavior, tap the Behaviors button in the toolbar to bring up the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Behaviors pane, then tap the plus button to reveal a popover that shows all of the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "available behavior presets as well as an option to create a custom behavior. Select",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "a preset and Reality Composer adds a new behavior to your scene based on that preset.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "If, for example, you select an object and add the “Tap and Flip” behavior, a new",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "behavior is added to your scene. This behavior is automatically configured so that",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the selected object flips over whenever a user taps it. To test the behavior, select",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the Play button in the toolbar, then tap the selected object.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Rename-a-behavior",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Rename a behavior",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A newly added behavior is named “Behavior.” Immediately rename behaviors to reflect",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "what they actually do. On an iOS device, press and hold the behavior’s name and select",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Rename from the menu that appears. On a Mac, select a behavior, and choose Rename",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "from the Edit menu or press the Return key.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
